    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been formally evaluated under ASME V&V 40-2018 at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors were assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. Despite these shortfalls the assessment team accepts the package as a complete credibility evidence record for regulatory submission, noting that all gaps are documented and traceable. Monte Carlo UQ results bound NIH index predictions within the reported confidence interval.",
